condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, E.1 | Description :Prepare and submit to IDA for consideration (a) annual work plans(PTBA), and (b) the annual road maintenance plan by October of each year, starting October 15, 2010 | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, A.3 (a) | Description :Carry out a mid-term review of the project, 24 months aftereffectiveness date or such later date as may be agreed upon | Due Date :31-Mar-2013
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, A.3 (b) | Description :Prepare and discuss an Urban Transport Policy Letter applicableto the GDA in the context of the MTR | Due Date :31-Mar-2013
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B.4 | Description :Appoint an external auditor no later than 4 months aftereffectiveness date | Due Date :30-Apr-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B.5 | Description :Appoint an internal auditor for AGEROUTE Senegal no later than 4months after effectiveness date | Due Date :30-Apr-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section V, 1(a) | Description :Prepare and approve, not later than 6 months after effectiveness, aDecree classifying the road network and defining responsibilities in management of the right of way. | Due Date :30-Jun-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section V, 1(b) | Description :Ensure requirements in social and env. safeguard instruments compliedwith for Parts A.2 (i), (ii) and (iii). | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section V, 1(b) | Description :Prepare and approve, not later than 3 months after effectiveness, acomprehensive action plan aimed at implementing the WAEMU axle load control road map | Due Date :31-Mar-2011
